title: No. 23 Tech closes Big 12 Championships in eighth place - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: No. 23 Tech closes Big 12 Championships in eighth place - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: No. 23 Texas Tech could not mount a rally to move up the leaderboard at the Big 12 Championships on Sunday as the Red Raiders dropped to an eighth-place finish following a 25-over-par 309 final round at The Clubs at Houston Oaks.
